  "task_id": "P37_prep_beta_barrel_membrane_1bxw",
  "task_intent": "Beta-barrel membrane protein preparation: prepare the transmembrane domain of outer-membrane protein A (OmpA) from PDB 1BXW embedded in a POPC lipid bilayer, excluding the crystallographic detergent (C8E), and neutralizing the system. This exercises membrane embedding for a beta-barrel architecture rather than an alpha-helical membrane protein.",
  "time_limit_minutes": 60
}
